          <a href="/join" class="text-sm text-neutral-500 hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300 no-underline">加入我们</a>
          <a href="/join#contact" class="text-sm text-neutral-500 hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300 no-underline">联系方式</a>
